<img src="../images/littleping.gif" align=right width=100 heigth=122>&nbsp;<b>Linux Mandrake</b> is based upon <b>Linux</b> the full 32 bits multitasking OS. It runs on most of Pentium and compatible architectures (Pentium, Pentium Pro, Pentium MMX, Pentium II, Pentium III and all clones). <i>Linux Mandrake</i> combines the power of Unix-based systems with the flexibiliy of a very powerful graphical Desktop-manager: KDE. It also includes many other graphical desktops like Gnome, AfterStep, WindowMaker, IceWM, XFCE, FVWM...<p align="justify">
It comes with the famous Apache Web Server, the Gnu Image Manipulation Program Gimp, Netscape Communicator and <b>many other</b> excellent software.
<b>Linux Mandrake</b> is free to get, free to use (please have a look at <a href=flicensing.php3>Licensing informations</a>), free to redistribute...<p>
Compatibility: <b>Linux Mandrake</b> is <b>99% compatible</b> with RedHat!<p>
Furthermore, our distribution is constantly updated with the new patches, and the new Linux Kernels.

